"title": "阿摩司書 1:1–2:16",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "30001001-30002016",
"language": "zht",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108562\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">阿摩司</span>宣講了針對<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108479\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">北國</span>周圍列國的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108534\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">審判的信息</span>，這些信息以<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108204\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">詩歌</span>的形式被紀錄了下來。這些詩歌是關於<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108434\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">大馬士革</span>的<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108540\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">亞蘭人</span>、<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108267\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">非利士人</span>和<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108475\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">泰爾</span>的居民，以及<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108411\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">以東人</span>、<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108412\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">亞捫人</span>、<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108397\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">摩押人</span>和<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108480\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">南國</span>的居民的。這些民族的土地位於一個圓圈中，北國位於這個圓圈的中心。接著，阿摩司談到了<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108199\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">神</span>也將對北國進行<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108233\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">審判</span>。</p>",
